located on the opposite side.

12
00:01:24,166 --> 00:01:26,583
Oh, no! What is she?

13
00:03:44,583 --> 00:03:48,375
How could you? Why, Sis?

14
00:03:55,541 --> 00:03:59,458
Activate Guild Build 2!
"I have control!"

15
00:04:09,750 --> 00:04:12,541
Please, Sis, why
are you doing this?

16
00:04:19,083 --> 00:04:20,458
Misa!

17
00:04:25,250 --> 00:04:29,000
No, don't! Please
stop! Stop this!

18
00:04:29,666 --> 00:04:32,083
Don't, Misaaa!

19
00:04:47,708 --> 00:04:48,583
Aki!

20
00:04:49,666 --> 00:04:51,708
Oh, no! You okay?

21
00:04:54,125 --> 00:04:57,166
Aki! Are you
having another atta-

