My sister. She disappeared.

24
00:05:20,041 --> 00:05:21,375
Oh, Aki.

25
00:05:24,125 --> 00:05:26,916
Breaking news: a new
solar storm has begun.

26
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:30,166
Its strength is unprecedented.
The storm, which broke at

27
00:05:30,250 --> 00:05:34,125
about 2:50p.m. has caused
electromagnetic interference.

28
00:05:34,208 --> 00:05:37,791
As you see, the storm has
had a worldwide impact already.

29
00:05:37,875 --> 00:05:40,541
It appears large-scale
explosions of unknown cause

30
00:05:40,625 --> 00:05:44,416
have occurred at the expo arena
which has been mostly destroyed.

31
00:05:49,791 --> 00:05:52,458
That bench. Let's sit
you down over there.

32
00:06:01,291 --> 00:06:03,416
That's new. What the?

33
